{"tid":360111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋非三大IT，人生有冇望?","createTime":"2017-08-15T04:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T04:41:24.000Z","uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5248ed197a2d03d9a411e8f6c5865beaab6a3fa","tid":360111,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到中大女生自殺一案，覺得自己人生更加無望。<br />\n<br />\n當年DSE 20分，衰咗一科語文，retake一年，21分入返U，雖然非三大，但嗰陣已經好開心好滿足。<br />\n但之後幾年，喺U識嘅朋友/同學，又真係有幾多個唔係私樓有錢。望番自己，有少少學歷又有乜野用，仲要成績咁差<br />\n<br />\n黎緊就黎畢業，我人生之後應該點好?<br />\n即使搵到份穩定嘅工，係咪又係做到死，機械式生活，為左層樓賣命?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s.唔鍾意去旅行，之前自費去過兩次，一次日本一次台灣，知道自己唔係鍾意四圍去既人，所以唔需要叫我去旅行散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04981505def7c04266cfc2e58b671f1cd614bf5","tid":360111,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25211ccd480d18f2da745e394a37e84e70aeca17","tid":360111,"uid":65778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦"},{"pid":"236c878783958bc4fdd3e076e4894953d2a3c7be","tid":360111,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁嫁啦</blockquote><br />\n開親個個post都咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪應該要改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}